    metaTitle: "What Is a Market Maker | Citadel Securities Explained | Ethics Reporter",
    metaDescription: "Market makers like Citadel Securities provide continuous liquidity in securities markets by quoting both buy and sell prices. The Ethics Reporter explains how market making works.",
