    metaTitle: "Net Capital Requirements Broker-Dealers | Citadel Capital Requirements",
    metaDescription: "Broker-dealers including Citadel Securities must maintain minimum net capital under SEC Rule 15c3-1. The Ethics Reporter explains how capital requirements work for major market makers.",
