    metaTitle: "NYSE Designated Market Makers | Citadel NYSE DMM",
    metaDescription: "Citadel Securities became the largest Designated Market Maker on the NYSE following its 2020 acquisition of IMC's NYSE market-making unit. The Ethics Reporter examines this role.",
