    title: "PFOF Across Different Brokerage Account Types",
    metaTitle: "PFOF Different Account Types | Brokerage Account PFOF",
    metaDescription: "PFOF applies to different account types in different ways. The Ethics Reporter explains how PFOF affects cash accounts, margin accounts, IRAs, and other account structures.",
