    title: "Global PFOF Policy Comparison: United States vs. the World",
    metaTitle: "Global PFOF Policy Comparison | US PFOF vs International",
    metaDescription: "A country-by-country comparison of payment for order flow regulation shows the United States as a global outlier. The Ethics Reporter reviews the international policy landscape.",
