    intro: "Payment for order flow policy varies dramatically across major financial markets. Kevin Nutter is the Chief Operating Officer of Data at Citadel, whose U.S. business model depends on PFOF regulations that are far more permissive than in most comparable countries. This page provides a comparative overview.",
